      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/cpb-pressure-head-comparison-001",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Pressure-head curve validation against bench measurements",
      "description": "Simulated pressure-head curves compared against in-vitro bench measurements at 5 flow-speed operating points. Mean absolute error 4.2%; all points within acceptance band. Validation performed using the same laminar steady-state model configuration deployed for hemolysis prediction. No sensitivity study on turbulence modelling was conducted."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/cpb-rh-index-comparison-002",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Relative hemolysis index comparison against predicate device data",
      "description": "Predicted relative hemolysis index (RH) values compared against published predicate device hemolysis data at matched operating conditions. RH < 1 for all 5 evaluated conditions. Validation activities used steady-state laminar flow fields; turbulence-driven shear stress contributions in the impeller discharge region were not represented in the simulation and were not evaluated in any validation sub-study."
    }
