      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under CPB-representative flow-speed envelope. Blood analog fluid used. Operating points span the COU envelope. Validation activities judged relevant to the COU. Note: the simplified laminar model used in validation is the same model applied in the COU; no turbulence fidelity assessment was performed within the validation program."
