      "rationale": "Solver convergence monitored; residuals below 1e-5 for continuity, momentum, and scalar transport equations at all operating points. Iterative error estimated negligible relative to discretization error. Not formally assessed as a separate factor at MRL 2 but convergence criteria documented."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
