      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters traceable to measurement or literature with documented uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Geometric inputs derived from CMM measurements of physical pump (tolerance ±0.01 mm). Fluid viscosity from rheometer measurements. Rotational speed and flow boundary conditions from calibrated instrumentation. Input uncertainty documented in uncertainty register UI-CPB-2023-02. Assessed as meeting required level."
    },
